666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> -уйда пропискада </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">турувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#11}Аризачининг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#12}Аризачига паспорт берилган худуд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> туман </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#13}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: right;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Ариза тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.4px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Нотариус идорасининг жойлашган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О. </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Ишончноманинг реестрда қайд қилинган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Ишончноманинг қайд қилинган реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақами билан қайд қилинган ишончноманинг аслини </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Ҳужжатнинг аслиги нима бўлганлиги тўғрисида маълумот</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сабабли ушбу ишончноманинг дубликатини беришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Имзо ________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Дубликатни олдим:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>____________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">Эслатма: </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">1. Васиятноманинг дубликатини беришдан олдин васият қилувчининг ўлганлигини тасдиқловчи маълумот олиниши лозим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">2. Дубликат сўралаётган ҳужжат автомототранспорт воситасига тааллуқли бўлса, «дубликатни» деган сўздан кейин «махсус (гербли) бланкада» деб қўшиб ёзилади.</span></p>\n</div></div>",
